    <td bgcolor="#FFFFCC"><p>SIR, </p>
      <p>Being a member of the committee to which the subject of vaccination has been referred, I ask of you the favour to say, if to do so meets your approbation, what you believe is the proportion of subscriptions and money received, by contributions to the vaccine institution, from the interior of the country and the towns and cities on the maritime frontier.&nbsp; Also, if you please, to say, what amount of subscriptions and receipts has been obtained from North Carolina, within the last six months. </p>
      <blockquote>
        <p>Your compliance will oblige, </p>
        <blockquote>
          <p>THOS. H. HALL. </p>
        </blockquote>
